<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1037736" n="5r"/>
<opener>Ad Patruum Johannem <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs>.</opener>
<p>
<lb/>Non mihi vitio vertes, Patrue honoratissime, quod nihil literarum ad Te hactenus miserim, 
                    <lb/><unclear>d</unclear>eque valetudinis Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> famili<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>que statu, quem tamen optime se habere confido, nihil interrogaverim; 
                    <lb/>tantum enim abest, ut officium hoc meum ex negligentia intermiserim, ut potius quotidie cogitave<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/><unclear>rim</unclear>, quid mihi factu opus esset, ut pro beneficiis acceptis debitas gratias agere, Tuumque favorem <lb/>ulterius demereri possem, sed rerum mearum status perplexissimus mihi hactenus ullas ad Te li<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>teras dare non permisit. Verum et nunc superfluum esse judico, ut observantiam erga Te 
                    <lb/>meam prolixis verbis exprimam, cum firmiter credam, Te animi mei candorem probe nosse, 
                    <lb/>satisque perspectum habere, quod <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> simulationibus longe sim alienus; sufficiat igitur mihi, 
                    <lb/>si Tibi persuaderi sinas, mihi nihil reliqui ad diligentiam futurum, quo mea erga Te officia 
                    <lb/><unclear>co</unclear>nstent. <choice><orig><g ref="#Agrav">À</g></orig><reg>A</reg></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-135542286" type="person">Patre</rs> meo sine dubio jam intellexisti, quomodo <rs type="person">discipulus</rs><!-- Schüler von Nic. I Bernoulli in Bern identifizieren.--> meus se hucusque gesse<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rit, quamque de ipso spem conceperim, sed res longe aliter cecidit ac putabam, ita ut ne<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sciam an diutius hic vivere dicam an languere velim. <rs type="person">Mater</rs><!--Mutter des Schülers von Nic. I B. identifizieren.--> tandem <rs type="person">filii sui</rs> voto satisfa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cere debebit, illumque, quia nullo modo adduci potest, ut <rs key="place_GEO-2661552" type="place">Bern<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> maneat, ad exteros, et 
                    <lb/>quidem ut credo mecum <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basileam</rs> proficisci sinet; gratum proin faceres, si illum hospitio 
                    <lb/>Tuo excipere velles, ut ob viciniam <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dium nostrarum eo facilius curam ejus habere possem. 
                    <lb/>Eclipses nuperas tam Solis<note>Sonnenfinsternis vom 28. Februar 1710. Espenak / Meeus, Five Millennium Catalog of Solar Eclipses, Cat.-Nr. 08812 <!-- https://eclipse.gsfc.nasa.gov/5MCSEmap/1701-1800/1710-02-28.gif --></note> quam Lun<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>,<note>Mondfinsternis vom 13. Februar 1710. Quellen: und Fred Espenak, Five Millennium Catalog of Lunar Eclipses, Cat.-Nr. 08941 <!-- https://eclipse.gsfc.nasa.gov/5MCLEmap/1701-1800/LE1710-02-13P.gif -->.</note> quas maximo desiderio expectabam, ob c<choice><orig><g ref="#oe">œ</g></orig><reg>oe</reg></choice>lum nubi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>losum observare non licuit, quod admodum doleo. <rs key="pers_DE-588-118634771" type="person">Wolfio</rs>, si nondum ad ipsius <rs key="B_1709-10-09_991170516539305501" type="letter">literas</rs>
<rs key="B_1710-04-26_991170516539205501" type="letter">re<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>spondisti</rs>, rogo ut meo nomine pro missa <rs type="biblio">Disputatione</rs><!-- werktag --><!--Wolff, Christian, Consideratio Physico-Mathematica Hiemis proxime praeterlapsae, hoc est, An. MDCCIX. Quam sub Ipsius Praesidio in Academia Halensi ad diem XIII. Iunii ejusdem Anni horis antemeriedianis in Auditorio Majori defendit Georgius Remus, Gedanensi, Halae Magdeburgicae (Chr. A. Zeitler) 1709.--> gratias agas, ipsumque <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>nisi hoc Tibi 
                    <lb/>fuerit inco<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>odum<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> ores, ut Cl. <rs key="pers_DE-588-118783181" type="person">Menckenio</rs> cultum meum deferat, eique significet, me 
                  <pb facs="1037737" n="5v"/>
<lb/>mirari, quod nullas cum Actis literas, nec earum pretium miserit. Cl. <rs key="pers_DE-588-116082356" type="person">Battierio</rs> nostro Ber<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nenses Professionem Juridicam offerre in animo habent, sed ter centum thaleri, in quibus 
                    <lb/>salarium Professoris Juris, ut dicunt, consistet, illum <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>ita persuasus sum<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> in hunc terr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> 
                    <lb/>angulum ex Academia in Scholam ignobilem, ex luce in tenebras pertrahere non vale<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bunt. Aliud quid novi, quod Tibi perscribi mereatur, jam non suppetit, quare has finio,
                    <lb/>Teque una cum <rs key="pers_DE-588-108991332X" type="person">honoratissima</rs> conjuge <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144 pers_DE-588-1153514060 pers_DE-588-118656503 pers_DE-588-1089913494" type="persons">liberisque</rs> charissimis quam plurimum salvere 
                    <lb/>jubeo. <rs key="place_GEO-2661552" type="place">Bern<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> d. <date when="1710-03-05">5. Martii 1710.</date>
</p>
